<div class="sub-title">Navigate the map</div>
<div class="text">
	All photos on sale on <b> GeoStockPhoto </b> are displayed in a navigable map.
	Move through the map by using the field "Search location" in the top men&ugrave!
	The photos will be displayed as thumbnails, small or large depending on the grade obtained.
	The map will not load more than 250 photos to keep the system efficient and a more comfortable navigation.
	On zoom or move, the map is reloaded with new photos. <br>
	To refine your search, click on Search location, and you'll see a form that will allow you to narrow down your search by:
	<ul>
		<li>Username of the photographer</li>
		<li>Vote</li>
		<li>Category</li>
		<li>Dimension</li>
		<li>License</li>
	</ul>
	Below the map, you'll see the best photos of the region displayed in the map.
</div>
<br>

<div class="sub-title">Select the photo</div>
<div class="text">
	Clicking on a thumbnail in the map or on one of the top photos below, you will update the box on the right with information about the selected picture.
	Within this box you can:<br>
	<ul>
		<li>Add the photo in your shopping cart.</li>
		<li>Show the enlarged photo in a lightbox (by clicking the thumbnail).</li>
		<li>Go to the page of the photo (by clicking <i>Details</i>).</li>
		<li>Go to the personal page of the photographer (by clicking his username).</li>
	</ul>
</div>